---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ThemeDemo from '../../components/ThemeDemo.svelte';
---

<Layout title="Theme - GlassUI">
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <div>
      <p class="text-sm font-medium text-primary mb-1">Components</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-foreground tracking-tight">Theme</h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-muted-foreground-2">
        Layered theme system: Preline base provides defaults (typography, colors, borders). GlassUI themes override 3 palette colors (<code class="text-xs bg-layer px-1 py-0.5 rounded">--theme-primary</code>, <code class="text-xs bg-layer px-1 py-0.5 rounded">--theme-secondary</code>, <code class="text-xs bg-layer px-1 py-0.5 rounded">--theme-accent</code>). Glass accents and glows auto-derive.
      </p>
    </div>

    <hr class="border-border" />

    <ThemeDemo client:load />
  </div>
</Layout>
